    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接一场神秘且充满挑战的冒险吧！O.W.L Projekt 是一款 3D 等距视角的益智游戏，它将考验你的思维能力和逻辑技巧。你将控制 Elysion，一个在神秘实验中创造的年轻存在，面对神秘的守望者，踏上逃脱和揭示秘密的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elysion 手持强大的 Sanctum 法杖，可以移动物体并克服障碍，为玩家提供独特且沉浸式的游戏体验。挑战自己，通关 50 个精心设计的关卡，每个关卡都具有创新机制和逐渐增加的难度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创新的益智机制：在 3D 等距环境中操作方块，拖动平台，发现秘密通道，攀爬梯子。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >渐进式挑战：每组关卡都引入新的挑战和机制，让游戏始终充满趣味和刺激。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的故事：跟随 Elysion 的逃脱任务，揭开实验项目背后的神秘守护者的面纱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的美学风格：享受引人入胜的视觉风格和令人着迷的关卡设计。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 个独特关卡：在 50 个不同的关卡中探索并解谜，每个关卡都提供独特且有回报的挑战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助 Elysion 逃脱，揭示他创造背后的秘密。利用 Sanctum 法杖的力量，移动高山（字面意思），克服路上所有的挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好挑战你的思维和逻辑了吗？开始 O.W.L Projekt 的冒险，看看你能否解开所有的秘密！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
